{"tid":1296531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果政府長期拖我哋有咩策略？","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:21:03.000Z","uid":173612,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"92a8436fe915a98272e78d4faadf65e8c9170dd0","tid":1296531,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:45:47.000Z","msg":"假如政府不斷拖我哋 我哋可以做啲乜？<br />\n無錯我哋可以keep住遍地開花 18區活動 但之後呢？如果政府都唔理 我哋可以點？我哋又點keep住而家呢種大家都關心政治呢一股風氣？ 如果我哋唔諗到一個方法 好快就會好似變成雨傘後咁 大家覺得失望同灰心 香港政治發展再沉靜 到時可能唔只五年<br />\n<br />\n我認為而家要開始諗定plan b 除咗爭取政府回應我哋五大訴求之外 我哋都應該要學吓點玩區議會同功能組別 以我住嗰區為例 長年係建制派拎到議席 唔係因為泛民選唔贏 係直頭無派人嚟選 我相信有唔小區都有咁嘅情況 所以我希望泛民或者想參選區議會嘅巴打巴可以留意呢啲區域。另外 功能組別方面 我哋其實一直唔識點玩 我哋唔識點樣去拎功能組別呢張選票或者出選功能組別 所以我希望熟悉呢方面知識嘅人可以好好講解 始終功能組別占咗一半 我哋唔理嘅話都係輸 惡法一樣通過<br />\n<br />\n希望大家一齊討論 我唔想今次大家咁努力 大家最後變成雨傘2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_GwKsJLqYLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_GwKsJLqYLc&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=43fb6555\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_GwKsJLqYLc</a><br />\n13:00開始"},{"pid":"11b6bb35231256be6ed83972764700fd62d89e62","tid":1296531,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re